DJ Stokie:
DJ Stokie have 9 songs on the Spotify Top 200 Weekly South Africa chart. 
 They first appeared on the chart on 2020-12-17. Their most recent appearance has been on 2024-01-18. They have a total of 16646390 million streams. 
. His highest position on the chart is 1 for the song Awukhuzeki which was at this position on 2023-08-17
 The songs of his that have appeared on the chart are Aw'ufani Nabanye ... Awukhuzeki ... Ipiano e'Soweto - Edit ... Masithokoze ... Ngaphandle Kwakho ... Soke S'bone ... Superman ... Ubsuku Bonke ... Waze wamuhle
